From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: sarun <noreply@sarun>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 18:37:31 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] find: defer output creation until execution preparation

Keep -fprint, -fprintf, -fprint0, and -fls destinations unresolved while the real argument parser builds its matcher tree. Prepare the tree only after complete successful parsing and help/version handling, resolving relative outputs through the injected logical cwd. This keeps parser replay effect-free and makes the preparation seam recursive through every logical matcher.

---
